features of the remote include signal-emitting led , on-off switch , mute button , nine channel buttons , two buttons for increasing or decreasing volume , two buttons for scrolling up or down channels and menu button at the centre , which would control the colour , sharpness , brightness etc .
also , there would be an elongated shaped swapping button that was slightly flexible .
if it was turned to the left , the tv would change to the previous channel that the user was watching and if to the right , the next channel .
the remote has an inbuilt voice recognizer that would recognize the user 's voice and act accordingly .
